title.rendered: How to unlock Acer, Gateway, PackardBell bios Password

content.rendered:
How to unlock Acer, Gateway, PackardBell  bios Password

If you have an Acer, Gateway, PackardBell 10 Decimal digits example 2039837875, we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will receive the Key from which the password can be calculated.

  • Please Type your Key example see picture ( 2039837875)
  • In this case the key is 10 digit decimal   ( 2039837875)
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your Key
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • After you receive the password turn off and ON again laptop and put your password

Price for unlock 1 unit Acer 10 digits password is: $14.00

If you have an Acer, Gateway, PackardBell 8 decimal digits example 74003099, we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will receive System disabled code from which the password can be calculated.

  • Please Type your Key  example see picture (74003099)
  • In this case, Key key is 8 digit hexadecimal   ( 74003099)
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your key
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • After you receive the password turn off and ON again laptop and put your password

  • Price for unlock 1 unit Acer 8 Digit key  is:  $6.00
